data.description: Wonderful 4 bedroom and 2 1/2 bath all brick home in Walnut Hill subdivision.  Home is freshly painted with new carpet throughout and features an extra two-car 24x30 (720 sq ft) detached garage that is heated and cooled by a dedicated HVAC system.  Extra garage is plumbed and has a sink for water usage This home features an oversized great room that flows into the kitchen with breakfast bar and eat-in area, extra-large pantry, large laundry room, and formal dining room.  Home also features an area in the walk-up attic area that can be finished as an additional bedroom or party room - 28x16.  An 18 x 15 rear deck is covered by an awning.  Home also features a fenced yard and sprinkler system.
